snippet.title: Feather Party Steam Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to chick planet! Chicks living on this planet love to play. So here you will find many different types of games! Fight alone against opponents! If you want, create private game rooms with your team. Then join Feather Party to play!
